title: Tootie's October 2014 Mix
description:
Tootie's October 2014 Mix is a return to the typical monthly Tootie mix. This mix is partially influenced by past and forthcoming events. They include the (Piersons') First Annual Summer Luau!, the 2014 Team Tootie vs. Team Kobashi Softball Game, the wedding of Chris Smiley and Joy Tutie, and the Team Silvia vs. Team Tootie Laser Tag Competition.

The method focuses on vocal volume.
